'''WKBA''' (1560 [[AM broadcasting|AM]]) and '''WKPA''' (1390 [[AM broadcasting|AM]]) are [[radio stations]] simulcasting a [[Gospel music]] format. Licensed to [[Vinton, Virginia]], and [[Lynchburg, Virginia]], USA, they serve the [[Roanoke, Virginia]], area.  The station is currently owned by [[Tinker Creek Broadcasters]]

